---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="Speaking & Events">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Speaking & Events</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 md:w-3/4 mb-4" style="line-height: 2">
        Where I've shared what I've learned and where I'm going next. Always happy to talk about building things.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <span class="i-lucide-mic w-4 h-4"></span>
        <span>Open to speaking opportunities</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Upcoming</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          I haven't spoken at any events yet, but I'm open to opportunities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          If you're organizing an event and think I'd be a good fit, let's talk. I love sharing what I've learned and learning from others.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">What I'd love to talk about</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">"Building Products That Matter"</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Potential Talk</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">The journey of building Larry SMS Hub and pivoting MarketMate</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>Lessons learned about user research, building for real problems, and the importance of simplicity in product design.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">"Learning to Code Without a CS Degree"</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Potential Talk</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">My self-taught journey and practical advice for new developers</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>Resources, building projects, and how to think about learning programming as a skill, not just a degree.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">"Building in Emerging Markets"</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Potential Talk</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">The unique challenges and opportunities of building tech in Ghana</p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>Understanding local context, payment systems, user behavior, and why global solutions don't always work locally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Topics I love talking about</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Product & Business</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>• Building products that solve real problems</p>
            <p>• User research and validation</p>
            <p>• The lean startup approach</p>
            <p>• Building for African markets</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Development & Learning</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>• Self-taught development journey</p>
            <p>• Modern web development tools</p>
            <p>• Building with simplicity in mind</p>
            <p>• Learning by building projects</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Entrepreneurship</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>• Starting with limited resources</p>
            <p>• Building in emerging markets</p>
            <p>• The importance of local context</p>
            <p>• Learning from failures</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Design & UX</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <p>• Designing for simplicity</p>
            <p>• Mobile-first thinking</p>
            <p>• Understanding user behavior</p>
            <p>• The power of good defaults</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Why I speak</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          I speak because I've learned things the hard way, and I want to help others avoid some of the mistakes I made.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          I believe in sharing knowledge openly. The best way to learn is to teach, and the best way to improve is to get feedback from others.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Plus, I love meeting other builders and learning from their experiences. Every talk is a chance to learn something new.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">What to expect</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Practical, not theoretical:</strong> I share real experiences, real mistakes, and real solutions that actually work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Honest about challenges:</strong> Building things is hard. I don't sugarcoat the difficulties, but I also share how to work through them.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Interactive and engaging:</strong> I prefer conversations over lectures. Questions and discussions make talks better for everyone.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Actionable takeaways:</strong> You'll leave with specific things you can try, not just inspiration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">Invite me to speak</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">See what I've built</a>
        <a href="/reading" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">What I'm reading</a>
        <a href="/resume" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">My background</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
